      "text": "The [[Bank of England]]  will finally allow non-bank ‘payment service providers’ (PSPs) to hold accounts at the Bank of England , so that they can compete with existing banks to provide current (checking) accounts - [http://positivemoney.org/2016/06/bank-of-england-uk-banks-to-lose-their-status-as-gatekeepers-to-the-payment-system/ positivemoney.org]"
    },
